            "title": "長沙灣寶馬轉彎失控撞毀鐵欄 司機杳然",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"寶馬失控撞毀鐵欄。梁國峰攝\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/52f20f8bb1a7fc089343bf6b1245caa2/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250517/_2025051708465239501.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">寶馬失控撞毀鐵欄。梁國峰攝</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>今(17日)早上7時15分，一部寶馬私家車沿長沙灣連翔道左轉入欽州街西期間，在長沙灣副食品批發市場對開，突失控猛撼路邊鐵欄，2米長欄杆被掃毀，寶馬車頭嚴重損毀，途人見狀報警求助，警員到場時發現人去車毀，司機已不在場，正設法聯絡車主了解事件。現場所見，寶馬司機位氣袋彈出，車內遺下多張未繳罰款告票。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4253463/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"寶馬失控撞毀鐵欄。梁國峰攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/626db5e298f2da1ac3d692ea9ff284be/2025-05/KakaoTalk_20250517_082356423_01.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        寶馬失控撞毀鐵欄。梁國峰攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4253464/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"司機已離開現場。梁國峰攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f4719bf6bf0af92411e809100ac3acc7/2025-05/KakaoTalk_20250517_082356423_04.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        司機已離開現場。梁國峰攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4253465/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"車廂內遺下多張告票。梁國峰攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/195da03b5b613e63f4104183b842dcb3/2025-05/KakaoTalk_20250517_082356423_05.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        車廂內遺下多張告票。梁國峰攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4253466/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"寶馬掃毀2米長鐵欄。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/d873fb35438fe7d07cdf8aed72471009/2025-05/KakaoTalk_20250517_082356423_06.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        寶馬掃毀2米長鐵欄。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4253467/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"寶馬車頭嚴重損毀。梁國峰攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/6a6d2e13400d3064e5ffef4311ca1460/2025-05/KakaoTalk_20250517_082356423_07.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        寶馬車頭嚴重損毀。梁國峰攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4253468/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"警員到場調查。梁國峰攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/3c8d291f90b67adb19208ec72bc7dafc/2025-05/KakaoTalk_20250517_082356423_08.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        警員到場調查。梁國峰攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
