        },
        {
            "title": "藍田德田邨5旬婦暈倒  家人發現惜返魂無術",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/a1407104fc56b24385b11838e33bb69e/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250517/_2025051707583518789.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\"></figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>今日（17日）凌晨零時許，藍田德田邨德樂樓一名52歲姓鄧女子在單位內暈倒，家人發現報警。救護員接報到場，將鄧女被送往聯合醫院治理，其後證實不治，\n\n</p>\n<p>據了解，女事主生前有身體病紀錄，其死因有待驗屍後確定。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2069353/即時-港聞-藍田德田邨5旬婦暈倒-家人發現惜返魂無術",
            "pub_date": "2025-05-17 08:06:31",
            "source": "stheadline",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "德甲 | 歐聯席位在望 波盤齊贏納「福」",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"法蘭克福中鋒伊基迪克能傳擅射，擅長策動反擊。路透社\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/4e46875bc82cca6e47633bad7d69234a/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250517/_2025051705300250344.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">法蘭克福中鋒伊基迪克能傳擅射，擅長策動反擊。路透社</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>德甲煞科日，現居第3位法蘭克福只要作客對第4的弗賴堡保持不敗，即可保住來屆歐聯參賽資格，以其近5場不敗兼只失3球的防守力，應能守住大門伺機反擊，而中鋒伊基迪克速度高兼擅長策動反擊，更有力波盤齊贏，今場讓球盤受讓平手半球「客勝」抵撐。 - 馬高\n\n</p>\n<p><br/>\n德甲在最後一周仍有3隊能爭奪最後兩個歐聯席位，法蘭克福分別領先緊隨其後的弗賴堡和多蒙特2分及3分，形勢佔優，今仗只要保持不敗，即能鎖定前4踢來屆歐聯。\n\n</p><h2>新星伊基迪克撐起法蘭克福</h2>\n<p>法蘭克福今場作客對直接競爭對手弗賴堡，可採最擅長的穩守突擊戰術，隊中射手中鋒伊基迪克今季已入22球兼有11個助攻，擅長策動反擊，配合前場其他速度高的攻擊手，形勢定如魚得水。\n\n</p>\n<p>弗賴堡近5場贏4場和1場，氣勢雖然不俗，惟對手幾乎全是踢風流波之流。再者，法蘭克福同樣保持5場不敗的近勢，兼5仗中只失3球，論防守力可頂得住主隊弗賴堡，只要把握到反擊機會，不難波盤齊贏。\n\n</p>\n<p><br/>\n<strong>星島推介<br/>\n弗賴堡 1:2 法蘭克福<br/>\n半場：0:0<br/>\nbeIN SPORTS CONNECT 今晚9:30直播</strong>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2069349/即時-體育-德甲-歐聯席位在望-波盤齊贏納-福",
            "pub_date": "2025-05-17 08:01:45",
            "source": "stheadline",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "車Cam直擊｜兩私家車觀塘道狂飆 警車尾隨展追逐戰",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/b0c759211a90ee1d76c273325aae37f4/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250517/_2025051707360746873.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\"></figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>今日(17日)網上流傳一段影片，拍到兩部私家車一前一後，在觀塘道往九龍灣方向狂飆，而後面有一輛警車窮追不捨，雙方展開激烈追逐戰。\n\n</p>\n<p>該段影片長約7秒，只見兩部私家車高速狂飆，而後面的警車則亮起閃燈，一路尾隨追截，三部車高速追逐的刺淚畫面剛巧被鄰線車輛的車Cam拍下。由於影片短促，未有交代兩私家車是否被截獲。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4253449/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ed65cca19ce102ff0bc5873585c1b6fd/2025-05/Screenshot_2025-05-17_at_12_19_00_AM.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4253450/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/b399d4c082c1e8cb395f3285156f3cbc/2025-05/Screenshot_2025-05-17_at_12_19_13_AM.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>有當時在馬路上的駕駛者批評該兩名私家車司機罔顧其他道路使用者的安全，如果當時自己未為意避開，恐怕後果不堪設想。\n\n</p>\n<p> \n\n</p>\n<p>警方表示，暫未有事件詳細資料。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2069352/即時-港聞-車Cam直擊-兩私家車觀塘道狂飆-警車尾隨展追逐戰",
            "pub_date": "2025-05-17 07:41:28",
            "source": "stheadline",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "罕見病︱福建3歲童頭頂兩巨痣  5個月兩施手術與「米奇老鼠」說再見",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"罕見病︱福建3歲童頭頂兩巨痣  5個月兩施手術與「米奇老鼠」說再見\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/0da20afb26bea90fa37438149fdaee85/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250516/_2025051618283193574.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">罕見病︱福建3歲童頭頂兩巨痣  5個月兩施手術與「米奇老鼠」說再見</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>福建3歲男童琪寶罹罕見病，頭上長出兩巨痣，遭人嘲笑是「米奇老鼠」。琪寶在上海治療五個月，經兩次手術，成功摘除自小惹來異樣目光的黑痣，開心的對著鏡頭說：「我最喜歡拍照了」。\n\n</p><h2>頭顱置入擴張器注水</h2>\n<p>綜合內媒及琪寶母親陳女士的抖音賬號，懷著琪寶時的產檢也沒有異常，直至分娩後，才發現琪寶患有先天性巨痣和多發痣，令琪寶一直承受外人奇異眼光的壓力。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4252160/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"接受第二次手術前琪寶要頂著「米奇老鼠」頭示人。抖音＠美俠小頭\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/8c6d3319a22ae6858ca30bedb8949e30/2025-05/A_001_2.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        接受第二次手術前琪寶要頂著「米奇老鼠」頭示人。抖音＠美俠小頭\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4252161/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"琪寶準備接受第二次手術，把頭上巨痣摘去。抖音＠美俠小頭\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/89a10c5e8808263e25c96af7793c2c37/2025-05/A_52652.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        琪寶準備接受第二次手術，把頭上巨痣摘去。抖音＠美俠小頭\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4252162/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"琪寶準備接受第二次手術，把頭上巨痣摘去。抖音＠美俠小頭\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/87987e3310fcafc3b42e9e2b082636ad/2025-05/B_52.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        琪寶準備接受第二次手術，把頭上巨痣摘去。抖音＠美俠小頭\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4252163/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"接受第二次手術前琪寶要頂著「米奇老鼠」頭示人。抖音＠美俠小頭\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/9f76e7bb701a9a6708564726d4066953/2025-05/B_62.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        接受第二次手術前琪寶要頂著「米奇老鼠」頭示人。抖音＠美俠小頭\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4252164/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"接受第二次手術前琪寶要頂著「米奇老鼠」頭示人。抖音＠美俠小頭\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/7c7a3b781f2a136842c3087c66151461/2025-05/B_5256.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        接受第二次手術前琪寶要頂著「米奇老鼠」頭示人。抖音＠美俠小頭\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4252165/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"摘去頭上巨痣後，琪寶開心的說「最愛拍照」。抖音＠美俠小頭\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/a119b50bd289902802162583e1586d2e/2025-05/B_5163564.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        摘去頭上巨痣後，琪寶開心的說「最愛拍照」。抖音＠美俠小頭\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4252166/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"接受第二次手術前琪寶要頂著「米奇老鼠」頭示人。抖音＠美俠小頭\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/d6efcfefb7227ca5f23836f9c98e820b/2025-05/Ktc7aCSqqpVsiF67LGlqAv12x-nitLMsvNGLRrzRi0Y.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        接受第二次手術前琪寶要頂著「米奇老鼠」頭示人。抖音＠美俠小頭\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4252167/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"琪寶為切除頭上巨痣，要在頭頂兩側注水，被人嘲笑是「米奇老鼠」。抖音＠美俠小頭\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/1a9a8fb624350a183a50060bb5ef84e8/2025-05/New_Project_23023.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        琪寶為切除頭上巨痣，要在頭頂兩側注水，被人嘲笑是「米奇老鼠」。抖音＠美俠小頭\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4252168/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"琪寶成功完成第二次手術，把頭上巨痣摘去。抖音＠美俠小頭\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/82c2362464316782cebd72047b8c0643/2025-05/OvbDQfHGAI0K5l6d8S8IZI7_LpxcVGeB3GDxQNxg8UA.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        琪寶成功完成第二次手術，把頭上巨痣摘去。抖音＠美俠小頭\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>相關新聞：<a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/realtime-world/3456108/%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E9%A6%96%E4%BE%8B-%E7%BE%8E%E7%94%B7%E5%AC%B0%E6%8E%A5%E5%80%8B%E4%BA%BA%E5%8C%96%E5%9F%BA%E5%9B%A0%E7%B7%A8%E8%BC%AF%E6%B2%BB%E7%99%82-%E7%82%BA%E7%BD%95%E8%A6%8B%E7%97%85%E6%82%A3%E5%B8%B6%E4%BE%86%E5%B8%8C%E6%9C%9B\">全球首例 | 美男嬰接個人化基因編輯治療 為罕見病患帶來希望</a>\n</p>\n<p>四出為琪寶求醫的陳女士，在五個月前帶兒子到上海，開始了前後五個月的漫長治療。由於琪寶要先經手術，在頭部兩側放入擴張器再注水，讓琪寶皮膚得以擴張，以便能覆蓋切除痣後頭部留下的空隙。\n\n</p>\n<p>陳女士：「他之前很難受，兩個包包頂著很小心翼翼，愈吹愈大，（頭皮像）氣球愈來愈薄，時刻擔心它（頭皮）破了」。\n\n</p><h2>難抵旁人奇異眼光</h2>\n<p>陳女士更難受的是，放入擴張器後，琪寶要承受痛楚之餘，還有旁人大驚小怪的目光，甚至被人冠以「米奇老鼠」綽號，被人不斷嘲笑和指指點點，令琪寶變得寡言，「就坐在他的推車裡然後就蓋住篷」不講話。\n\n</p>\n<p>近日，琪寶捱過多個月的身心理不適，終於迎來「解脫」，成功完成第2次手術，把頭頂兩個大如氣球的巨痣摘除。<br/>\n<br/>\n相關新聞：<a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/realtime-world/3412901/%E6%97%A9%E8%A1%B0%E7%97%87%E8%BA%AB%E9%AB%94%E6%AF%8F%E5%B9%B4%E8%80%818%E6%AD%B2-%E5%8D%97%E9%9D%9E%E5%B0%91%E5%A5%B319%E6%AD%B2%E9%9B%A2%E4%B8%96%E7%94%9F%E5%91%BD%E5%8A%9B%E9%A9%9A%E4%BA%BA\">早衰症｜身體每年「老8歲」 南非少女19歲離世生命力驚人</a>\n</p>\n<p>陳女士透露，琪寶後續還需進行多次修覆手術。手術後的影片顯示琪寶頭部纏著繃帶，快樂地在醫院的嬰兒室裡玩耍，擺脫奇異外貌的琪寶，在病床上還開心的對著鏡頭表示「最喜歡拍照」。\n\n</p>\n<p>據台灣罕見疾病基金會的說明，巨型先天性黑色素痣的定義為一種良性、非癌化、由黑色素細胞(melanocyte)組成直徑大於20厘米的痣(nevus)，是由皮膚中產生色素細胞異常過度生長所引起。\n\n</p>\n<p> \n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
